         <ttm:title>Creating an eOffer</ttm:title>
         <ttm:desc>To create an eOffer, select a Solicitation against which the Offer will be submitted. You will need to have completed a few preliminary qualifications in order to begin the eOffer creation process.
         </ttm:desc>
