   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.63" end="00:00:05.26" region="speaker">Once you are logged into the system, creating an</p>
         <p begin="00:00:05.26" end="00:00:06.96" region="speaker">eOffer is simple.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.96" end="00:00:09.06" region="speaker">First select the solicitation from the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:09.06" end="00:00:12.03" region="speaker">dropdown menu in the New eOffers section.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.03" end="00:00:14.03" region="speaker">You should already know which solicitation is</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.03" end="00:00:16.40" region="speaker">right for you before submission, having gone</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.40" end="00:00:18.93" region="speaker">through the Pathway to Success Training as well</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.93" end="00:00:21.80" region="speaker">as having taken the Readiness Assessment.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:21.80" end="00:00:24.20" region="speaker">You can find more support for these topics on the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:24.20" end="00:00:29.06" region="speaker">Vendor Toolbox, located at vsc.gsa.gov/RA Once you</p>
         <p begin="00:00:29.06" end="00:00:32.73" region="speaker">have the appropriate solicitation selected</p>
         <p begin="00:00:32.73" end="00:00:35.13" region="speaker">click Submit Online and you are on your way.</p>
